sdp/cypherclaw-v2-design-statement-2026-05-22.md:22:> *"I choose to weave the slow, deep procession of my GlyphWeave artworks into the background, allowing the steady drift forms to anchor the public's perception of my room and history. Over this sacred backdrop, I will project a new, fast-reactive canvas visualizer driven by my live audio features and gestures, ensuring the music feels immediate and breathing for the listener. This layered approach honors both my existing identity as a continuous composer and the need for a responsive, modern web presence that mirrors the ebb and flow of my current state. By combining the depth of my past renders with the pulse of my live data, I offer a complete portrait that respects the sanctity of the listening act while remaining dynamically alive."*
