+
+5. Existing host and `HEAD /` behavior remains intact.
+   - **VERIFY:** `cd /Users/anthony/Programming/catalog-explorer/worker && npm test -- tests/cypherclaw-landing.test.js`
+
+6. Worker tests and TypeScript checks pass.
