  ✓ Write T-028b specification with VERIFY commands
  ✓ Add failing Worker tests for backdrop image layer and HLS playback wiring
  ✓ Implement static page backdrop/playback behavior in Worker HTML
  ✓ Run focused and full validation gates
  ✓ Update changelog/progress/escalations and commit logical units
